the hall, open--

00:02:45.845 --> 00:02:48.840 align:middle line:84%
well, I turned the light on,
and then I'd walk to the window

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:50.820 align:middle line:84%
and I'd say, good
morning, girls.

00:02:50.820 --> 00:02:54.360 align:middle line:84%
And I'd open this very heavy
curtain that would then go up.

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:56.408 align:middle line:84%
And one morning, it
was a cold morning.

00:02:56.408 --> 00:02:58.200 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to get
out of bed right away.

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:00.270 align:middle line:84%
And I was still
thinking about dreams

00:03:00.270 --> 00:03:01.920 align:middle line:90%
and daydreaming a little bit.

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:04.200 align:middle line:10%
And in my mind, I was
daydreaming that I walked down

00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:05.970 align:middle line:10%
the hall, turned
on the light, said,

00:03:05.970 --> 00:03:07.977 align:middle line:10%
good morning, girls,
opened the curtain.

00:03:07.977 --> 00:03:10.560 align:middle line:10%
And I thought, well, wouldn't
it be great if it was that easy?

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:12.850 align:middle line:84%
But then I hear noises
from their room.

00:03:12.850 --> 00:03:15.043 align:middle line:84%
And then they come
running around the house,

00:03:15.043 --> 00:03:15.960 align:middle line:90%
and they're like, Mom?

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:16.410 align:middle line:90%
Mom?

00:03:16.410 --> 00:03:17.340 align:middle line:90%
Where are you?

00:03:17.340 --> 00:03:19.470 align:middle line:84%
They said, Mom, what are
you doing back in bed?

00:03:19.470 --> 00:03:21.600 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS] I never got out of bed.

00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:22.452 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:03:22.452 --> 00:03:24.300 align:middle line:90%
And I said, what?

00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:25.170 align:middle line:90%
What do you mean?

00:03:25.170 --> 00:03:26.070 align:middle line:90%
You just saw me?

00:03:26.070 --> 00:03:27.060 align:middle line:90%
And they said, yes.

00:03:27.060 --> 00:03:28.180 align:middle line:90%
I said, where was I?

00:03:28.180 --> 00:03:30.345 align:middle line:90%
And they said, in our room.

00:03:30.345 --> 00:03:32.310 align:middle line:84%
