00:03:33.720 --> 00:03:37.050 align:middle line:84%
And their light is on, the
window curtain is open,

00:03:37.050 --> 00:03:39.110 align:middle line:84%
and nobody else
could have done that.

00:03:39.110 --> 00:03:41.370 align:middle line:90%
It only could have been me.

00:03:41.370 --> 00:03:45.150 align:middle line:84%
And I know I didn't, so I
experienced that I'm in bed.

00:03:45.150 --> 00:03:46.890 align:middle line:90%
They experienced I was there.

00:03:46.890 --> 00:03:49.170 align:middle line:84%
So that was what a
bilocation felt like.

00:03:49.170 --> 00:03:52.770 align:middle line:84%
And for me, daydreaming and just
sort of wishing I was there.

00:03:52.770 --> 00:03:54.523 align:middle line:84%
The other time it
happened, I was

00:03:54.523 --> 00:03:56.190 align:middle line:84%
daydreaming and wishing
I was somewhere,

00:03:56.190 --> 00:03:57.780 align:middle line:90%
and someone saw me there.

00:03:57.780 --> 00:04:00.330 align:middle line:90%
So I've done this twice.

00:04:00.330 --> 00:04:01.493 align:middle line:90%
And it feels great.

00:04:01.493 --> 00:04:03.660 align:middle line:84%
It's just feeling like, ah,
I wish I could be there.

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:04.710 align:middle line:90%
And then guess what?

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:05.610 align:middle line:90%
Maybe you are.

00:04:05.610 --> 00:04:07.770 align:middle line:10%
So after this
experience happened,

00:04:07.770 --> 00:04:11.280 align:middle line:10%
I immediately looked up
to see what could explain

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.610 align:middle line:10%
these kind of experiences.

00:04:12.610 --> 00:04:16.440 align:middle line:84%
And I found out that
throughout history, people have

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:18.040 align:middle line:90%
had these kinds of experiences.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.560 align:middle line:90%
It's really quite normal.

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:24.090 align:middle line:10%
And it's something that
is considered often

00:04:24.090 --> 00:04:27.150 align:middle line:10%
something that's typical
for a shaman or someone who

00:04:27.150 --> 00:04:30.240 align:middle line:10%
is the healer for a
