There's a tremendous change
that occurs energetically,

00:28:40.690 --> 00:28:44.620 align:middle line:84%
as well as with the focus of
my attention, which goes from--

00:28:44.620 --> 00:28:47.080 align:middle line:84%
usually being humans, we're
looking at, what's wrong?

00:28:47.080 --> 00:28:48.610 align:middle line:90%
What's not going right?

00:28:48.610 --> 00:28:50.860 align:middle line:84%
What's the thing that's a
little bit off right now?

00:28:50.860 --> 00:28:52.000 align:middle line:90%
We tend to focus on that.

00:28:52.000 --> 00:28:53.920 align:middle line:84%
But instead, by
bringing your attention

00:28:53.920 --> 00:28:56.785 align:middle line:84%
back to what's really good,
what are the blessings?

00:28:56.785 --> 00:28:58.660 align:middle line:84%
What are the things that
mean the most to us,

00:28:58.660 --> 00:29:00.070 align:middle line:90%
that we're grateful for?

00:29:00.070 --> 00:29:05.500 align:middle line:10%
Then we get this boost of energy
and also a boost of a focus.

00:29:05.500 --> 00:29:07.345 align:middle line:84%
It definitely brings
us back on track.

00:29:07.345 --> 00:29:09.960 align:middle line:90%


00:29:09.960 --> 00:29:12.270 align:middle line:90%
And forgiveness does this too.

00:29:12.270 --> 00:29:14.020 align:middle line:84%
Some people have trouble
with forgiveness,

00:29:14.020 --> 00:29:15.750 align:middle line:84%
but if you can do it,
that's a good one.

00:29:15.750 --> 00:29:17.790 align:middle line:84%
Forgive yourself
and forgive others.

00:29:17.790 --> 00:29:20.353 align:middle line:84%
Forgiveness can be
easier when you recognize

00:29:20.353 --> 00:29:22.770 align:middle line:84%
like in "A Course of Miracles"
that there's nothing to it,

00:29:22.770 --> 00:29:27.100 align:middle line:84%
that everybody is already a
pure being of consciousness

00:29:27.100 --> 00:29:28.830 align:middle line:84%
and a pure being
of light and love,

00:29:28.830 --> 00:29:30.690 align:middle line:90%
and that's who we really are.

00:29:30.690 --> 00:29:32.320 align:middle line:90%
And we tend to forget that.

00:29:32.320 --> 00:29:35.730 align:middle line:84%
So sometimes people have trouble
really feeling like, really?

00:29:35.730 --> 00:29:38.505 align:middle line:84%
That seems-- that can be
a stretch for some people

00:29:38.505 --> 00:29:40.188 align:middle line:90%
to go that far.

00:29:40.188 --> 00:29:41.730 align:middle line:84%
But if you can do
it, it's wonderful,

00:29:41.730 --> 00:29:45.120 align:middle line:84%
because the benefit
is phenomenal.

00:29:45.120 --> 00:29:46.950 align:middle line:84%
Because what happens
when we don't forgive,

00:29:46.950 --> 00:29:48.570 align:middle line:84%
we don't notice
that we're getting

00:29:48.570 --> 00:29:52.000 align:middle line:84%
pulled down with these
negative feelings of something

00:29:52.000 --> 00:29:52.800 align:middle line:90%
went wrong.

00:29:52.800 --> 00:29:54.660 align:middle line:84%
And if only that hadn't
happened, if only

00:29:54.660 --> 00:29:56.110 align:middle line:90%
they didn't do that.

00:29:56.110 --> 00:29:59.550 align:middle line:84%
But when you let go of it,
it's also very expansive

00:29:59.550 --> 00:30:03.590 align:middle line:84%
to go into forgiveness
and gratitude and love.

00:30:03.590 --> 00:30:06.180 align:middle line:90%
Those are very powerful.

00:30:06.180 --> 00:30:08.880 align:middle line:84%
One thing we can do is
putting yourself back

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:11.520 align:middle line:84%
into the center of the
story, because sometimes we

00:30:11.520 --> 00:30:13.530 align:middle line:84%
get caught thinking
we're a victim

00:30:13.530 --> 00:30:16.020 align:middle line:84%
or we think something
has happened to us.

00:30:16.020 --> 00:30:19.290 align:middle line:84%
And the way to
break free of that,

00:30:19.290 --> 00:30:22.680 align:middle line:84%
it's basically a drama
triangle, because then it's

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:24.750 align:middle line:84%
just playing games and
pretending that you're

00:30:24.750 --> 00:30:27.420 align:middle line:84%
wearing the role of victim and
someone else is the villain,

00:30:27.420 --> 00:30:29.400 align:middle line:90%
and there might be a rescuer.

00:30:29.400 --> 00:30:31.590 align:middle line:84%
But when you realize, that
doesn't make any sense.

00:30:31.590 --> 00:30:35.460 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to retrain
my subconscious that I

00:30:35.460 --> 00:30:37.300 align:middle line:90%
can do whatever I want to do.

00:30:37.300 --> 00:30:39.910 align:middle line:84%
I can be the hero
in my own story.

00:30:39.910 --> 00:30:44.280 align:middle line:84%
But not the kind of hero
where I'm fighting evil.

00:30:44.280 --> 00:30:48.210 align:middle line:84%
Just recognizing that I can
bring about changes that I

00:30:48.210 --> 00:30:49.300 align:middle line:90%
want to see in the world.

00:30:49.300 --> 00:30:51.070 align:middle line:84%
I can be that
change in the world.

00:30:51.070 --> 00:30:54.130 align:middle line:84%
And when you really feel like
you're doing what you love,

00:30:54.130 --> 00:30:55.980 align:middle line:90%
then you can come fully alive.

00:30:55.980 --> 00:30:58.110 align:middle line:84%
And you'll find people
that are excited to be

00:30:58.110 --> 00:31:01.010 align:middle line:90%
with you, doing that too.

00:31:01.010 --> 00:31:05.630 align:middle line:84%
This idea of shifting the Earth
with shared intent, with shared

00:31:05.630 --> 00:31:08.600 align:middle line:84%
consciousness, and the reason
I keep calling it dreaming

00:31:08.600 --> 00:31:10.280 align:middle line:84%
is because when we
think intention,

00:31:10.280 --> 00:31:12.170 align:middle line:90%
we tend to stay in our heads.

00:31:12.170 --> 00:31:15.170 align:middle line:84%
When we dream, we dream
with our fullness of being.

00:31:15.170 --> 00:31:17.550 align:middle line:84%
And in our dreams
we can take action,

00:31:17.550 --> 00:31:19.833 align:middle line:84%
which we can then feel
and give voice to,

00:31:19.833 --> 00:31:20.750 align:middle line:90%
and then we can think.

00:31:20.750 --> 00:31:25.160 align:middle line:84%
And so that's the way to bring
about the biggest changes

00:31:25.160 --> 00:31:26.220 align:middle line:90%
that we need to make.

00:31:26.220 --> 00:31:29.360 align:middle line:84%
And so sharing a
dream is actually

00:31:29.360 --> 00:31:31.490 align:middle line:90%
the way to transform the world.

00:31:31.490 --> 00:31:34.310 align:middle line:84%
And sharing a positive
dream, looking

00:31:34.310 --> 00:31:35.900 align:middle line:84%
at how good things
can get, which

00:31:35.900 --> 00:31:38.180 align:middle line:84%
is a question that I
like to leave open-ended

00:31:38.180 --> 00:31:40.670 align:middle line:84%
so we don't assume that
we know what it is.

00:31:40.670 --> 00:31:44.420 align:middle line:84%
And that way, you know
that good can prevail,

00:31:44.420 --> 00:31:46.910 align:middle line:90%
that good will be there.

00:31:46.910 --> 00:31:49.310 align:middle line:84%
And it matches the
fact that we live

00:31:49.310 --> 00:31:52.380 align:middle line:84%
in such a fine-tuned
universe right now,

00:31:52.380 --> 00:31:55.050 align:middle line:90%
which is ridiculously unlikely.

00:31:55.050 --> 00:31:58.760 align:middle line:84%
So some people say this is
proof that God exists, and I

00:31:58.760 --> 00:32:00.130 align:middle line:90%
tend to think so too.

00:32:00.130 --> 00:32:03.410 align:middle line:84%
I also think that we can
definitely see evidence

00:32:03.410 --> 00:32:06.680 align:middle line:84%
in that, that we're already
winning against whatever

00:32:06.680 --> 00:32:10.370 align:middle line:84%
may seem like it's impossible
or unsolvable or too

00:32:10.370 --> 00:32:12.860 align:middle line:90%
difficult or too evil.

00:32:12.860 --> 00:32:15.260 align:middle line:84%
The idea that what
resists persists

00:32:15.260 --> 00:32:19.460 align:middle line:84%
is really central to this idea
of dreaming a new reality.

00:32:19.460 --> 00:32:22.160 align:middle line:84%
If you're fighting something,
it seems like it gets stronger

00:32:22.160 --> 00:32:23.520 align:middle line:90%
or it hangs on--

00:32:23.520 --> 00:32:26.490 align:middle line:84%
in America, we have a war on
drugs that never seems to end.

00:32:26.490 --> 00:32:28.817 align:middle line:84%
We have so many wars,
so many conflicts.

00:32:28.817 --> 00:32:30.650 align:middle line:84%
And it seems like every
time we look around,

00:32:30.650 --> 00:32:32.360 align:middle line:90%
there's a new enemy.

00:32:32.360 --> 00:32:34.970 align:middle line:84%
But that's not really
the way to move forward

00:32:34.970 --> 00:32:36.650 align:middle line:90%
in a positive manner.

00:32:36.650 --> 00:32:38.210 align:middle line:84%
The way to move
forward positively

00:32:38.210 --> 00:32:41.390 align:middle line:84%
is to find what you are
grateful for, what you love,

00:32:41.390 --> 00:32:44.120 align:middle line:84%
and to bring more
of that into being.

00:32:44.120 --> 00:32:46.670 align:middle line:84%
So it's very obvious,
but it's something

00:32:46.670 --> 00:32:48.110 align:middle line:90%
that I think we're learning.

00:32:48.110 --> 00:32:50.540 align:middle line:84%
And this is part of that
global awakening right now.

00:32:50.540 --> 00:32:54.990 align:middle line:90%


00:32:54.990 --> 00:32:57.750 align:middle line:84%
I believe we do have
free will, but then this

00:32:57.750 --> 00:32:59.640 align:middle line:84%
comes back to that
question of consciousness

00:32:59.640 --> 00:33:03.000 align:middle line:84%
and who am I, which is
like the ultimate question.

00:33:03.000 --> 00:33:07.200 align:middle line:84%
So on some levels, if I
factor in the infinite,

00:33:07.200 --> 00:33:09.660 align:middle line:84%
eternal part of
myself that was here

00:33:09.660 --> 00:33:13.110 align:middle line:84%
before I was born, that
will be here after I die,

00:33:13.110 --> 00:33:15.780 align:middle line:84%
then that part of me has
an awareness of what's

00:33:15.780 --> 00:33:18.960 align:middle line:84%
going on that to me
in my day-to-day life

00:33:18.960 --> 00:33:23.340 align:middle line:84%
might feel like I'm living
a path of fate or something,

00:33:23.340 --> 00:33:25.570 align:middle line:84%
like things are meant
to be a certain way.

00:33:25.570 --> 00:33:29.130 align:middle line:84%
But we definitely do
experience free will every time

00:33:29.130 --> 00:33:31.410 align:middle line:90%
we can make a choice and choose.

00:33:31.410 --> 00:33:33.760 align:middle line:90%
Like, all these realities exist.

00:33:33.760 --> 00:33:34.950 align:middle line:90%
Let's try that one.

00:33:34.950 --> 00:33:36.630 align:middle line:90%
Then we can give it a try.

00:33:36.630 --> 00:33:38.880 align:middle line:84%
And when it comes
to neuroscience,

00:33:38.880 --> 00:33:41.670 align:middle line:84%
what scientists are
noticing strangely,

00:33:41.670 --> 00:33:43.650 align:middle line:84%
it gets back to that
question of time,

00:33:43.650 --> 00:33:46.590 align:middle line:84%
because we're noticing
sometimes that we've

00:33:46.590 --> 00:33:48.960 align:middle line:84%
made a decision
before we've even

00:33:48.960 --> 00:33:52.830 align:middle line:84%
felt the input to our senses,
which seems impossible.

00:33:52.830 --> 00:33:54.930 align:middle line:84%
But as far as my
own experience, I

00:33:54.930 --> 00:33:58.858 align:middle line:84%
feel like we do have free
will and that it matters.

00:33:58.858 --> 00:34:00.900 align:middle line:84%
I think that's the most
important thing right now

00:34:00.900 --> 00:34:04.210 align:middle line:84%
for us as humans to deal with
all the problems on the planet

00:34:04.210 --> 00:34:06.330 align:middle line:84%
and to help each
other, is to recognize

00:34:06.330 --> 00:34:08.880 align:middle line:84%
the level of expansiveness
that we can attain

00:34:08.880 --> 00:34:12.570 align:middle line:84%
and the way that we can play
with these different realities.

00:34:12.570 --> 00:34:15.435 align:middle line:90%
And also share consciousness.

00:34:15.435 --> 00:34:17.310 align:middle line:84%
As we were talking about
healing someone else

00:34:17.310 --> 00:34:20.040 align:middle line:84%
and sharing a dream, we
can pull each other up

00:34:20.040 --> 00:34:23.170 align:middle line:84%
by sharing positive
dreams with one another.

00:34:23.170 --> 00:34:25.260 align:middle line:84%
And that can be
extremely empowering

00:34:25.260 --> 00:34:29.639 align:middle line:84%
and can pull us out of
things that look impossible.

00:34:29.639 --> 00:34:31.853 align:middle line:84%
We don't live in a
linear timeline at all.

00:34:31.853 --> 00:34:34.020 align:middle line:84%
I think that is one of the
biggest things for people

00:34:34.020 --> 00:34:38.010 align:middle line:84%
to realize, is that you're
able to see what you might call

00:34:38.010 --> 00:34:39.750 align:middle line:90%
a miracle in a moment.

00:34:39.750 --> 00:34:41.219 align:middle line:90%
Anything could happen.

00:34:41.219 --> 00:34:43.889 align:middle line:84%
And to recognize that
there's always a possibility

00:34:43.889 --> 00:34:46.409 align:middle line:90%
for phenomenal transformation.

00:34:46.409 --> 00:34:48.820 align:middle line:84%
And people who have
been aware of this--

00:34:48.820 --> 00:34:51.580 align:middle line:84%
and even if you're skeptical,
you can still get this to work.

00:34:51.580 --> 00:34:54.630 align:middle line:84%
So next time you're in
a difficult situation--

00:34:54.630 --> 00:34:56.857 align:middle line:84%
maybe the car is out of
gas or you're stranded

00:34:56.857 --> 00:34:58.690 align:middle line:84%
or you have no money
or you lost your purse,

00:34:58.690 --> 00:35:01.800 align:middle line:84%
or whatever happened,
some sort of bad news--

00:35:01.800 --> 00:35:02.800 align:middle line:90%
just take a moment.

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:03.600 align:middle line:90%
Relax.

00:35:03.600 --> 00:35:04.400 align:middle line:90%
Meditate.

00:35:04.400 --> 00:35:05.280 align:middle line:90%
Center yourself.

00:35:05.280 --> 00:35:06.690 align:middle line:90%
Breathe.

00:35:06.690 --> 00:35:09.690 align:middle line:84%
And then just imagine, well,
how good could this get?

00:35:09.690 --> 00:35:12.060 align:middle line:84%
And imagine, just
like it's a dream,

00:35:12.060 --> 00:35:13.890 align:middle line:84%
like you're going
into that daydream

00:35:13.890 --> 00:35:16.270 align:middle line:84%
and you're going to
walk into that reality.

00:35:16.270 --> 00:35:19.350 align:middle line:84%
And so many people have
had phenomenal success,

00:35:19.350 --> 00:35:20.760 align:middle line:90%
doing exactly that.

00:35:20.760 --> 00:35:23.190 align:middle line:84%
And I share stories
about this in my book

00:35:23.190 --> 00:35:26.077 align:middle line:84%
"Quantum Jumps," because it
happens to so many people.

00:35:26.077 --> 00:35:28.160 align:middle line:84%
Even if you're skeptical,
even if you think, well,

00:35:28.160 --> 00:35:29.730 align:middle line:84%
that's ridiculous,
how could this

00:35:29.730 --> 00:35:32.130 align:middle line:84%
possibly work, this is
impossible-- the car's

00:35:32.130 --> 00:35:34.980 align:middle line:84%
out of gas, my wallet's
gone, whatever.

00:35:34.980 --> 00:35:36.720 align:middle line:84%
They've told me no,
they said they lost

00:35:36.720 --> 00:35:38.250 align:middle line:90%
my order, whatever happened.

00:35:38.250 --> 00:35:40.380 align:middle line:84%
But if you just
imagine, well, what

00:35:40.380 --> 00:35:43.950 align:middle line:84%
if there's just some chance
that maybe things are OK?

00:35:43.950 --> 00:35:46.020 align:middle line:90%
There's a slim chance somehow.

00:35:46.020 --> 00:35:46.840 align:middle line:90%
Just believe in it.

00:35:46.840 --> 00:35:47.640 align:middle line:90%
Dream it.

00:35:47.640 --> 00:35:50.280 align:middle line:84%
And the dreaming is
so important, again,

00:35:50.280 --> 00:35:53.440 align:middle line:84%
because you're activating
the fullness of your being.

00:35:53.440 --> 00:35:55.440 align:middle line:84%
The trouble that some
people have with intention

00:35:55.440 --> 00:35:56.850 align:middle line:84%
is they're just thinking
with their heads,

00:35:56.850 --> 00:35:58.030 align:middle line:90%
and that doesn't work.

00:35:58.030 --> 00:36:00.910 align:middle line:84%
So you have to really get
a full embodiment of it,

00:36:00.910 --> 00:36:01.710 align:middle line:90%
of all of you.

00:36:01.710 --> 00:36:04.520 align:middle line:90%


00:36:04.520 --> 00:36:08.450 align:middle line:84%
People who feel like
they're absolutely stuck,

00:36:08.450 --> 00:36:11.730 align:middle line:84%
they are perfect proof of
this process in action.

00:36:11.730 --> 00:36:12.650 align:middle line:90%
That's true.

00:36:12.650 --> 00:36:15.020 align:middle line:84%
And it's true for
all of us, anybody

00:36:15.020 --> 00:36:16.310 align:middle line:90%
who is a human right now.

00:36:16.310 --> 00:36:17.550 align:middle line:90%
And that's me too, you know?

00:36:17.550 --> 00:36:18.880 align:middle line:90%
Nobody's perfect.

00:36:18.880 --> 00:36:20.930 align:middle line:84%
We all get to some point
where we believe, like,

00:36:20.930 --> 00:36:24.380 align:middle line:84%
well, this is too much,
or this is too difficult.

00:36:24.380 --> 00:36:26.480 align:middle line:84%
But at least I
know on some level

00:36:26.480 --> 00:36:28.030 align:middle line:90%
that that's not really true.

00:36:28.030 --> 00:36:30.080 align:middle line:84%
It's just that I've
grown up in a society,

00:36:30.080 --> 00:36:32.300 align:middle line:84%
on a world, on a planet
where that's been

00:36:32.300 --> 00:36:34.490 align:middle line:90%
the prevailing belief so far.

00:36:34.490 --> 00:36:36.795 align:middle line:84%
But I believe that that's
changing right now,

00:36:36.795 --> 00:36:38.420 align:middle line:84%
and more and more
people are waking up.

00:36:38.420 --> 00:36:42.670 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

